headline: CITGO Helps Gulf Coast Communities Prepare for Hurricane Season
summary: CITGO Petroleum Corporation is reinforcing its commitment to the safety and well-being of Gulf Coast communities by providing financial support to several hurricane preparedness initiatives in its operational areas, including Lake Charles, Louisiana, and Houston and Corpus Christi, Texas.
